Dialogs.Dialog: Ah, just a friend. We were just talking.
You know, maybe it's been a while since we've talked to each other properly.
Because you seem busy. So busy to seeing your girlfriend.
Haha, does it look that way？
It does. Well then, I'll be on my way before I keep you from her.
I wonder if they can see us talking like this.
You should at least talk with me once in a while.
Do you feel that having a girlfriend will make your life more enjoyable？
I need some help with something... Well, don't hold back because you have a girlfriend.
You know what？ It would be terrible if you neglect your work as a committee member because you're too busy with your girlfriend.
I wonder what it feels like to have a boyfriend... What, you got a problem with that？
I can hear you talking about your girlfriend. That's too good for you.
How is your relationship going？ Oh, you don't have to tell me after all.
Ah. I want to live a lazy, playful life...
Do you go on dates on your days off？ Dates, huh.
I read an interesting book recently... Well, do you have more interesting things to do？
Hey, what's it like to live alone？ Well, I guess you don't feel lonely because you have your girlfriend.
Balancing club activities and being a committee member is impossible for me... I'll try though.
A part-time job sounds great. I might want to try it.
Yes, I'm gonna do it, ▲小早川＊▲.
I see, you are working diligently.
I don't know. If you do mine, I'll believe it.
Don't get carried away. Help me out here.
Hey, are you busy at work？
Well, just getting by. Not so busy.
Oh, you already did that. Good job.
Aren't you pushing yourself too hard, ▲主人公＊▲？
Are you worried about me, ▲小早川＊▲？
Who's that？ The only who needs to worry about you is your girlfriend.
How's it going？ Yeah, I'm good. No problems.
Keep up the good work and reduce my workload.
You're on your own with that.
Let me help you with something, ▲主人公＊▲.
Oh, I changed my mind. I won't move from here.
By the way. How are things with your girlfriend？ Is everything okay？
Yes, yes, thanks for the food.
My hunch was right. You should have known better.
...Well, it's fine. Be a good boyfriend.
What？ ...Oh, you got a ▲特別デートアイテム＊＊▲.
Even if I had it, you know... I wondered if you would use it.
That's helpful, but... is it okay？
I don't mind. I'm sure your girlfriend will be happy, don't you？
I know it's weird that I'm the one who has to do this, but...
You have a girlfriend, but you talk to me a lot, don't you？ Is it okay？
Yeah, maybe it's bad for my girlfriend...
I see, I thought so. Was I too insensitive？
I see, sounds like you can handle it. Makes me wonder.
You know, we haven't talked properly for a while.
If it's not too much trouble... Can I talk to you again？
I think that's bad for my girlfriend...
So it's okay. Hehe, I'll do it then.
You know, lately... Have you changed in any way？
It's not the look, it's the feel.
What can I say, like a warm personality.
You see, you are cooler these days.
Aggressive, I mean. It feels like that.
Um, has your girlfriend changed her hair？
How, you say. You can tell by looking at her. It's for your sake, isn't it？
Good grief, it's hard to be a girlfriend with a boyfriend like this.
You know, I heard your girlfriend...
Lately, she's looking even better than before.
A reputation to live up to. You're a lucky guy.
It must make you feel bad... you know.
Isn't your girlfriend feeling down lately？
I don't want to meddle, but you know, I'm just curious.
You went home with your girlfriend again. I saw.
You seem to be very close.
I don't mean that as a compliment.
You mean "we"？ Ah, why did you say "like that"？
(No way, I think she's talking about skinship...)
I remember now. I witnessed your date.
I wasn't peeking. It's just a coincidence.
Haha, I know what you mean. We've been doing that a lot lately...
Oh dear, I'm not going to listen to your ramblings.
That's it, I feel bad for your girlfriend.
It's not possible to do that at school...
You seem to be on a roll these days, ▲主人公＊▲.
You have a reputation, as a guy who can do anything.
You are surprisingly like that, aren't you？
(Come to think of it, I've had a lot of success lately...)
Did something happen with your girlfriend？
Eh... I think she's fine, but why？
I felt like something was not going well...
How are you and your girlfriend these days？
We're getting by, it's all fine.
I know you're trying to be generous, but you're not naive enough to say you're just getting by.
You seem to be getting along well with your girlfriend lately.
I can see that. It's fine as long as you get along with each other.
Aren't you too close？ Is that what lovers do？
It's not weird, but... maybe too much to look at. Well, I guess it's a good thing.
(You must mean us being all lovey-dovey...)
I hope I'm wrong but, did something happen with your girlfriend？
You have a face like it's the end of the world.
Ugh... I don't know what you're doing. You're the cause of the problem anyway.
Come to think of it, I haven't emailed her lately...
Then that's it. You must miss her, you have to text her.
Why don't you just send it to her？ It's not like it's a hassle.
I knew that was the one...
Well, I guess I haven't kissed her lately...
Don't say those things to me... You idiot.
Maybe it's because I stood up for our date.
Apologize quickly, I say. Maybe you should make up for that date？
The last time I left my girlfriend alone on a date, she left...
If I did something like that, I'd have to apologize anyway.
Come to think of it, I have not seen my girlfriend much lately...
Why don't you contact them？ They might want to see you, too.
Your girlfriend doesn't seem to be doing so well, does she？
Maybe they are pushing themselves too hard. Maybe it's because of you.
I heard your girlfriend's out with a cold？
Are you gonna visit her？ I'm sure she'll be happy to see you.
A visit, huh... I guess so.
We went out together... quite a while ago. We are...
That was when you didn't have a girlfriend yet.
I think so. What about it？
Nothing. I'm just saying it because I remembered. What did you think it was？
Well... I guess nothing in particular.
I don't think you've forgotten about it...
I confessed to you, didn't I？
Yeah... that's right. Of course, I haven't forgotten.
And now, you have a girlfriend and... we are friends like this.
Well, I'm glad you're my friend.
You're on your way home now, right？ If you're free, do you want to go home with me？
I'm going home with my girlfriend
I'm a little busy, but it's okay.
I don't know what you're talking about. You're not busy.
I'm going home with my girlfriend.
Oh, I'm going home alone today.
Oh, I see. There are times like that.
It's okay. I just happened to meet a friend and we were talking.
Well, okay, then. Then, let's go.
...You know what, will you go home with me again？
Or course, huh. Well, that's it.
Heh, I guess you care about that kind of thing too, ▲小早川＊▲.
What do you mean "too"？ You don't want my chocolate？
Oh, you'll give it to me？
I don't think so. Your girlfriend is more than enough.
White Day, huh, it's tough having a girlfriend.
It's not that hard, though. It's just another event.
Hmmm, a generous statement. I lost money worrying about it.
You know... today is my birthday.
...That's all there is to it. Yeah, that's all I'll ever get.
Nothing. I just wanted to make a point.
You remembered, thank you. Don't tell me you got me a present too？
Idiot, there is no way. Who would do such a thing to a girlfriend？
I'm sure it's a busy day to have a girlfriend.
Don't fail and don't let them hate you. Good luck.
I see, a present for your girlfriend.
Yes, you're a girl too, right？ Help me out, ▲小早川＊▲.
I'm a decent girl, you know？
Of course. So, please help me out.
Hah, you are such an unreliable boyfriend to latch on to your kouhai.
Whatever. I can't help it, so I'll go out with you.
That's a big help！ Then, I'll rely on you.
It's ▲苗字▲. I have a favor to ask you.
I see, a gift for your girlfriend...
I beg you. I'd like to hear what you girls think.
So, you're saying it's for me. Well, is it okay？
That's a big help！ Then, I'll rely on you.
Sorry for asking you to come out so suddenly, ▲小早川＊▲.
It can't be helped. It's because onii-chan is an unreliable boyfriend！
Don't say that. Well, I'm counting on you.
Oh, that one might be good！
There you are. What are you doing？
Ah, it's just that she found me, and then ▲彼女＊＊▲...
You saved me today, thank you.
You're welcome. I hope you'll take my advice and make the right decision.
Well, then, we'll leave it at that.
Hmm, doesn't sound like you're alone？
Are you shopping for the tennis club or something.
It's for your part-time job today, or something like that？
Hmm. Well, that's okay. Rinko will be on her way.
Hey, have you been taking care of your girlfriend lately？
Well, in my own way... that is why you worry about me ▲小早川＊▲？
It's because you're sloppy. You're always depending on your girlfriend, aren't you？
I knew it. It's your fault.
I'm talking about your girlfriend. She's too good for you.
Yes, it is, I don't know how she can be in a relationship with you. I'm impressed.
Hah, I feel bad for your girlfriend.
I don't know. I'm sure she can find someone better.
Don't be so down. Come on, keep up the good work！
(Are you belittling me or encouraging me...)
She's doing fine... I think... No, she's doing awesome！
Wow... that's it. She's getting her boyfriend all worked up. She's not well- trained.
Yes, she seems perfect, but I think she's not quite ready to handle boyfriends.
(You seem to be proud of yourself.)
Hehe. Hey, can I spoil you？
That's was sudden. I don't mind... No, wait. I have a girlfriend, and she's ▲彼女＊＊▲.
Idiot, don't be so easily fooled！
Because, if she asks you, you'll do whatever she wants, right？
My girlfriend isn't so selfish. Unlike you, ▲小早川＊▲.
You think？ But don't you listen to a lot of requests？
I think your girlfriend is a good person.
Don't you think I'm a pretty good woman, too？
Wait, what's with that！ You're being rude.
(Well, she seems like a nice girl.)
I wonder if I'm not good enough.
What, that doesn't sound like you.
Because even someone like you has a great girlfriend, but when it comes to me, I'm just a...
Well, I don't really need a boyfriend.
You know, keep up the good work！
You always think you might not be good enough for her, don't you？
Don't worry. You might even shine a little if you polish yourself up！
Listen, if I'm in trouble, will you help me？
Hehe. That's reassuring. You're going to help even if you have a girlfriend？
Heh, you say that. I hope it's not all talk.
Having a girlfriend sounds like fun, but it also sounds like a lot of work. I wonder if you were pushing yourself too hard.
I'll be fine then！ It's not hard to push myself for the sake of my girlfriend！
Yes, yes, that's for the speech. I lost my hearing.
How are you doing these days？ Are you still lovey- dovey as usual？
Ouch, why did you do that？
